\f0\b \cf2 Transition:  You might not think this is a big deal but it is huge!  Because this is where many people get messed up in their walk with God\'85treating all passages the same and never understanding that God speaks to us in different ways at different times.  \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So if you would look at my relationships with my kids you could pull of these out\'85\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1
\f0\b \cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}One-Time Promises\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl2
\f1\b0 \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Me telling the kids that because I love them I\'92m going to take them to Holiday World\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Moses and the stick\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1
\f0\b \cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}All-Time Promises\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl2
\f1\b0 \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Illustration of me loving my kids no matter what they do\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Jesus died for everyone for all time\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1
\f0\b \cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}One-Time Promises that are All-Time Principles\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl2
\f1\b0 \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Illustration of me giving the kids a treat because they were good.\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is the passage we have today.\
