\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 GOD\
\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf5 \'a0
\f0\b\fs18 \super 7\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Ever since the time of your ancestors you have turned away\'a0from my decrees and have not kept them. Return\'a0to me, and I will return to you,\'94\'a0says the\'a0Lord\'a0Almighty.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}How\'92s your relationship with God today?  Honestly?  Is it what you want?  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is the question we have to ask daily\'85not just on Sundays but as we arise in the mornings\'85what do we want our relationship with God to be today\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So if you read this whole book it is a letter from God to His people and He is trying to draw them back.  \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \'93But you ask,\'a0\'91How are we to return?\'92\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What do you think God\'92s answer should be?  \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Pray more?  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Read the Bible more?  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Show up to church more!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 8\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub \'93Will a mere mortal rob\'a0God? Yet you rob me.\
\
\'93But you ask, \'91How are we robbing you?\'92\
\
\'93In tithes\'a0and offerings.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}During this time period there was an agreement that they would give God back (that being the key word) 10% plus offerings which was giving to the poor and homeless, feast and festivals and stuff like that which in total was about anywhere between 25% to 30% roughly of their gross, not net, income.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God is telling them they are robbing him and they don\'92t see it that way.  \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There are two ways to look at your money.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl1
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Owner \'96 It is mine, I made it, and God is like a man on the street looking for a handout that you feel guilty about and so you tip him as you walk into the store to buy your stuff with your money.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Steward not an owner - God gave us everything we have and we are stewards of what He has loaned us.  It is his land we plow and in turn He has rented it out to us for a 10% return.\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It is God\'92s world He created, He created you, your abilities, your skills, your work ethic, really everything and all He says is I\'92d like 10% back.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He could have said the other way around\'85I\'92ll take 90% and you keep 10% but he didn\'92t.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God says it is the latter and they are not giving Him what they owe Him.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You would do the same thing if someone rented a field from you and you agreed that you would get 10% of the profit but at the end of the year he didn\'92t it to you.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You would feel robbed.   Or if you work in sales you are suppose to get 10% of all that is sold\'85but they didn\'92t give it to you.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \'a0
\f0\b\fs18 \super 9\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub You are under a curse\'97your whole nation\'97because you are robbing me.\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God says I\'92ve cursed you because you are not with me\'85you are robbing me and I\'92m no longer investing in you until you quit.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And here\'92s His solution:\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 10\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Bring the whole tithe\'a0into the storehouse,\'a0that there may be food in my house. \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God tells His people, not anyone else, this is to His people only\'85you want to be good with me\'85bring me the WHOLE tithe\'85that there may be food in my house.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 Test me in this,\'94 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Money is a test!  God says you can test me because I\'92m testing you!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The reason this is so important is because we are constantly failing in this area in our relationship with God\'85and it clouds everything else!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 says the\'a0Lord\'a0Almighty, \'93and see if I will not throw open the floodgates\'a0of heaven and pour out\'a0so much blessing\'a0that there will not be room enough to store it.\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0
\f2 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They believed that their blessings came from the ground up but God says they come from Heaven down. \'a0\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And you know this intuitively because you\'92ve had seasons in your life when you were working harder and maybe even making more money but it went out the window. \'a0Cars broke down, air conditioners went out, hospital bills\'a0kept coming in\'85you\'92ve had those seasons.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 One person gives freely, yet gains even more; another withholds unduly, but comes to poverty.  Proverbs 11:24\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But then to hammer home the point he says\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 11\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub I will prevent pests from devouring\'a0your crops, and the vines in your fields will not drop their fruit before it is ripe,\'94 says the\'a0Lord\'a0Almighty.\'a0Malachi 3\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can live with 90% blessed or 100% cursed\'85which do you want?\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 Transition:  So what do you do with this?  Do you still have to tithe?  What\'92s my next step in this area\'85\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs32 \cf3 It\'92s a One-Time Promise with an All-Time Principle\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls13\ilvl0
\f3\fs28 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If\'a0we love God we will use money to get closer to God, if we love money we will use God to get more money\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls13\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What that means is you can trust it but it may not work out the way you want.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 APPLICATION:\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls14\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}View money as a test\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Embrace Grace\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Evaluate where your heart is in your budget this week\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Figure out a floor not a ceiling\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Follow the principle not your feelings\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 The 1 objections to this today:\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls15\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God just wants my money\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 CLOSING:\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 The single worst thing you can do in the area of your finances is to think it isn\'92t a test.  That it is neutral\'85it\'92s just money and no big deal.  That somehow where and how you spend your money is not spiritual.  It is a huge deal and it is constantly fighting for your heart whether you realize it or not.  \
\
